lyrics:
[verse]
In Barcelona's metro, a tale of the streets
Carteristas roam, plotting their feats
Silent as shadows, they strike with precision
Stealthy pickpockets, causing incision

[chorus]
Unseen hands in motion, beware the artistry
As they dance through the crowd, with criminal glee
Carteristas of the metro, a notorious crew
Their nimble fingers steal, leaving victims askew
